en_496148_0	Three people have been arrested for photographing the postal vote using a mobile telephone, while they were casting the vote.
en_496148_1	They have been arrested from Kekirawa and Katugastota areas.
en_496148_2	Among them are two teachers and a watcher of a school.
en_496148_3	Meanwhile, investigations have launched on several people who have photographed the postal ballot papers and published them over social media.
en_496148_4	The Elections Commission has requested the public to refrain from such activities.
